data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home in the highly sought-after Gem Heights neighborhood! This move-in ready home boasts 1,852 square feet of living space and is situated on a spacious 8,953 sq foot lot. The low-maintenance terraced backyard is perfect for relaxing or entertaining. You’ll love the peaceful private street and the park right across from you!  Inside, the main floor offers plenty of living space for all your needs. Upstairs, you’ll find four generously sized bedrooms, including a expensive primary suite with a full bathroom and your own private balcony! The location is conveniently located near shopping and freeways. Don’t miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this house your home!
